tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE deep_learning_experiments_metadata (
    experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(255),
    model_name VARCHAR(255),
    dataset_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE experiment_metadata (
    experiment_id INT NOT NULL,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    experiment_description TEXT,
    experiment_owner VARCHAR(100),
    experiment_start_date DATE,
    experiment_end_date DATE,
    PRIMARY KEY (experiment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE model_results (
    model_id INT NOT NULL,
    model_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    model_type VARCHAR(100),
    model_accuracy FLOAT,
    model_loss FLOAT,
    model_parameters TEXT,
    PRIMARY KEY (model_id)
);

CREATE TABLE hyperparameters (
    experiment_id INT NOT NULL,
    model_id INT NOT NULL,
    learning_rate FLOAT,
    batch_size INT,
    optimizer VARCHAR(100),
    epochs INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (experiment_id, model_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES experiment_metadata(experiment_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES model_results(model_id)
);

CREATE TABLE experiments (
    experiment_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    start_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    end_date TIMESTAMP,
    status VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'In Progress'
);

CREATE TABLE results (
    result_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id INT REFERENCES experiments(experiment_id),
    model_id INT REFERENCES models(model_id),
    accuracy FLOAT,
    loss FLOAT,
    evaluation_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE experiments (
    experiment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    start_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    end_date TIMESTAMP,
    status ENUM('running', 'completed', 'failed'),
    accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE models (
    model_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    model_type ENUM('CNN', 'RNN', 'GAN') NOT NULL,
    framework VARCHAR(50),
    hyperparameters JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE datasets (
    dataset_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    dataset_type ENUM('image', 'text', 'audio') NOT NULL,
    size_in_gb DECIMAL,
    created_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE experiments_results (
    result_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id UUID NOT NULL,
    model_id UUID NOT NULL,
    dataset_id UUID NOT NULL,
    execution_time INTERVAL,
    loss FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES experiments(experiment_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES models(model_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (dataset_id) REFERENCES datasets(dataset_id)
);

CREATE TABLE experiment_logs (
    log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id UUID NOT NULL,
    log_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    log_message TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES experiments(experiment_id)
);
